        data-tooltip='This was supposed to be relatively simple. But it&apos;s <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wdyndb17K58" target="_blank">Stripe</a> we&apos;re talking about <span class="text-white">ðŸ™‚</span> I&apos;ve ran into most of the issues described in that video and many more during this project. Migrating from one instance to another is a hell that made me into the man I&apos;m today.'
